Package uk.pallas.systems.typr.entities.v1.validation

Interface EnumValidationRule

All Superinterfaces:
ValidationRule
public interface EnumValidationRule extends ValidationRule
Some field definitions have a limited number of allowed string values and so this definition allows us to maintain a list rather than a regular expression.
